          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "format": 1,
            "content": "<p><strong>Source:</strong> Anime 5E Beyonder Worlds, PDF pp. 40, 48-49.</p><p>Science fiction support centers on advanced technology, spacefaring societies, alien Species, new Classes such as Gadgeteer, and gear ranging from blasters to starships and personal computers.</p>"
