            "content": "<p><strong>Source:</strong> Anime 5E Beyonder Worlds, PDF p. 94.</p><p>Urban fantasy brings magical action into modern spaces, where hidden supernatural factions, Technomancers, secret societies, monsters, and city-scale mysteries can coexist with contemporary life.</p>"
