            "content": "<p><strong>Source:</strong> Anime 5E Beyonder Worlds, PDF pp. 142, 144-148.</p><p>Modern Earth material supports contemporary action, spy stories, modern weapons and armour, specialised spy tech, and vehicles that bridge everyday reality with Anime 5E-scale adventure.</p>"
