    {
      "name": "Beyonder Worlds: Genre Configuration Notes",
      "folder": "Beyonder Worlds - Genre Guides",
      "pages": [
        {
          "name": "Configuration Notes",
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "format": 1,
            "content": "<p><strong>Source:</strong> Anime 5E Beyonder Worlds, PDF pp. 4, 14, 38, 148-151.</p><p>Beyonder Worlds content is isolated in this standalone module so science fiction, mecha fantasy, urban fantasy, cyberpunk, and modern Earth options do not populate fantasy-only base compendiums.</p><p>Use the module character-options pack for modern skills, new Attributes, new Defects, Species, and Classes. Use the module item pack for modern weapons, advanced armour, spy gear, cyberpunk equipment, vehicles, starships, and mecha. Vehicle and mecha Items retain source fields for size, AC, HP, passengers, speed, operators, and major systems.</p>"
          }
        }
      ],
